name: POWER
description:
Borning yourself, arouse courage inside of you, being aware of your power and potential is like passing through the door of a house which is full of power,love and life. If you desire to find that home, just call it back from the ocean of your soul and century-old memory. If you achieve this, difficulties won't be obstacle for you.
(1000*1350px, 1250dpi, Digital Painting made by Procreate 1/1)
